    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "The Nutcracker | Les Grands Ballets Canadiens | Nov 26 - 29, 2026 | Southam Hall"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40367/les-grands-ballets-casse-noisette-photo-sasha-onyshchenko-danseuse-aurora-de-mori__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "With the NAC Orchestra\n\nA Delight for All Ages\n\nLes Grands Ballets Canadiens’ The Nutcracker has been a family tradition since choreographer Fernand Nault created it in 1964. Inspired by Hoffmann’s tale and danced to Tchaikovsky’s sparkling, picturesque music, this classic is a glorious holiday gift. \n\nFollow young Clara and her charming Prince to the Land of Snow and the Kingdom of Sweets, where they find a bevy of larger-than-life characters: the Snow Queen, the King of Sweets, the Sugar Plum Fairy, cotton candy angels,..."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "728780803"
      }
    ],
