    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "El español sigue al texto en inglés\n\nEnjoy a free, music-filled midday break in the O'Brien Atrium. Bring your meal, grab a spot, and experience incredible live performances by talented artists—it's the perfect way to recharge over a lunch break! \n\nFormed in 2017 through late-night jam sessions and rogue rooftop gigs, Empanadas Ilegales is a psychedelic tropical music collective made up of musicians with roots in Colombia, Ecuador, Argentina, and Canada. Their music is both homage and invention: cumbia meets surf rock,..."
      }
    ],
