      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Three things to know: Among Igor Stravinsky’s most cinematic scores, The Firebird was heard in movie theatres around the world in Disney’s Fantasia 2000. Inspired by jazz, blues, and ragtime, George Gershwin’s concerto for solo piano..."
