    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Be whisked away to Scotland in a musical postcard depicting the country&rsquo;s enchanted landscape, while powerful settings of Toni Morrison&rsquo;s poetry mix elements of jazz and spirituals."
